---
description: Signal Lab stack constraints
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use Next.js App Router, Tailwind, shadcn-style UI components, TanStack Query, and React Hook Form in frontend changes.
- Use NestJS + Prisma + PostgreSQL in backend changes.
- Do not add Redux, SWR, Sequelize, TypeORM, or non-required alternatives.
- Keep observability components aligned with Prometheus, Loki, Grafana, and Sentry.
